'''Ange-Régis Hounkpatin''', ni Umufaransa - Umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] akaba n'umwanditsi . <ref>https://www.unifrance.org/annuaires/personne/409195/ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i Cotonou, muri [[Bene|Bénin]]. <ref name="augohr">http://augohr.de/catalogue/pantheon </ref>

== Umwuga ==
Nyuma yo kurangiza amashuri yisumbuye, Hounkpatin yimukiye mu [[Bufaransa]] kwiga ubuvanganzo. Amaherezo yinjiye mu ishuri rya Femis rya sinema muri 2009. Yakoze filime ''Rêves de intare'' mu mwaka wa nyuma  aza gutsindira igihembo cy'urubyiruko mu iserukiramuco rya Côté Court of Pantin mu 2014<ref>https://time-art.com/talent/ange-regis-hounkpatin.htm</ref>. Filime ye ''Cage'' yahisemo mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Champs-Élysées mu 2016. Mu mwaka wa 2015, yakoze filime ''Vindicte'' yafatiwe muri Bénin maze atoranywa mu iserukiramuco rya Devant Festival rya Paris mu 2016. <ref name="augohr">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://augohr.de/catalogue/pantheon "Panthéon: A Film by Ange-Régis Hounkpatin"]. augohr<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo cyiza cya Cinematografiya mu iserukiramuco rya Filime ryabereye i Toronto . <ref>https://matthewtoffolo.com/2018/07/20/interview-with-filmmaker-ange-regis-hounkpatin-vindicte/</ref><ref>https://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/409195/ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref>

Muri 2017, yayoboye filime ye ya gatanu ngufi ''Pantheon'' . Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi ihitamo kumugaragaro kugirango yerekane iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika 2017, iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Atlanta 2018 na Filmfest Dresden 2018<ref>http://tsproductions.fr/film/pantheon-ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref>. Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Bridging the Borders muri Palm Springs International Festival ya Filime ngufi 2017<ref>http://tsproductions.fr/film/pantheon-ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref>. Muri uwo mwaka, filime yakiriye icyubahiro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Kolkata. <ref>http://tsproductions.fr/film/pantheon-ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref>

